<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-11-30T05:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-11-30T05:00:00-05:00" n="592" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d592">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">893.61331/239: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Grew</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-11-30T19:00:00+09:00">November 30, 1940—7
                                        p.m.</date><lb/>[Received December 1—4:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>1245. Our 1212, November 27, noon,<note n="43" xml:id="d592fn43">See
                                    footnote 38, <ref target="#pg_551">p. 551</ref>.</note>
                                Universal Leaf Tobacco Company. In conversation with the Foreign
                                Minister today, I repeated our representations of November 27 in an
                                effort to impress the Minister with the particularly flagrant
                                character of this case of interference with the legitimate and long
                                established rights of this company. Mr. Matsuoka made notes of my
                                remarks and said that he would pursue the matter.</p>
                            <p>Sent to the Department via Peiping. Peiping please repeat to
                                Chungking, Tientsin and Tsingtao.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>